  "text": "A pharmacist should be a member of and actively participate on committees responsible for establishing policies and procedures for medication use, patient care, and performance improvement, among other things. [CITATION_1] Pharmacists should also participate in the activities of similar committees of a parent home infusion organization or health system, as applicable.",
